<div class="animatedwrapper">
  <div class="dot dot--one"></div>
  <div class="corner-dot"></div>
  <div class="dot dot--two"></div>
  <div class="dot dot--three"></div>
</div>

<header>
  <h1>Hello, I'm Chiara.</h1>
  <h2>I'm a web developer.</h2>

  <p id="header-subtext">I create web applications mainly on Rails & Javascript.<br>I'm looking for my place in the world somewhere between <strong>creativity</strong> and <strong>logic</strong>.</p>
  <p id="callTA"><strong>Take a look at some of my projects.</strong></p>
</header>

<main class="container">
  <div class="static-dot"></div>
  <div class="projects">

    <div class="project-card row">
      <div class="description col-12 col-xl-6">
        <h3 class="project-title">Book a Cook</h3>
        <div class="project-links">
          <% link_to "https://bookachef.herokuapp.com/" do %>
            <i class="fas fa-link"></i></i>
          <% end %>
          <% link_to "https://github.com/OoKiaoO/book-a-cook" do %>
            <i class="devicon-github-original"></i>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="project-description">
          <p><strong>Team Project</strong></p>
          <p><strong>Main Role:</strong> Front-end development, UI/UX Desing</p>
          <p>Book a Cook is an Airbnb-style app that connects culinary professionals with on-demand requests from customers and brings their business directly to their homes.</p>
          <div class="dev-icons">
            <i class="devicon-rails-plain-wordmark"></i>
            <i class="devicon-javascript-plain"></i>
            <i class="devicon-sass-original"></i>
            <i class="devicon-bootstrap-plain-wordmark"></i>
            <i class="devicon-postgresql-plain-wordmark"></i>
            <i class="devicon-heroku-original-wordmark"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot mockup col-12 col-xl-6">
        <% link_to "https://bookachef.herokuapp.com/" do %>
          <%= image_tag "BookaCook.png" %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card row">
      <div class="description col-12 col-xl-6">
        <h3 class="project-title">Nicotine Derby</h3>
        <div class="project-links">
          <% link_to "http://www.nicotinederby.money/" do %>
            <i class="fas fa-link"></i></i>
          <% end %>
          <% link_to "https://github.com/OoKiaoO/Habitat" do %>
            <i class="devicon-github-original"></i>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="project-description">
          <p><strong>Team Project</strong></p>
          <p><strong>Main Role:</strong> Front-end development, UI/UX Desing, Authentication</p>
          <p>A mobile-first application designed to help smokers reduce the number of cigarettes smoked.</p>
          <div class="dev-icons">
            <i class="devicon-rails-plain-wordmark"></i>
            <i class="devicon-javascript-plain"></i>
            <i class="devicon-sass-original"></i>
            <i class="devicon-bootstrap-plain-wordmark"></i>
            <i class="devicon-postgresql-plain-wordmark"></i>
            <i class="devicon-heroku-original-wordmark"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="project-mockup col-12 col-xl-6">
        <div class="mobile mockup">
          <% link_to "http://www.nicotinederby.money/" do %>              
            <%= image_tag "ND-profile.PNG" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about">
    <div class="about-me row">
      <div class="bio col-12 col-lg-8">
        <h3>Hi there!</h3>
        <p>My name is Chiara and I'm a Tokyo-based full-stack developer with a background in Travel and Customer Care. I used to travel the world for a living out of the middle eastern desert, until I decided to move to Japan to focus on my career in travel, but ended up a developer instead..Oops.</p>
        <p>I create web applications from scratch using mainly Ruby on Rails and Javascript and very much enjoy curating the UI and UX design as well, which is why I end up taking care of the design part in most of my Team projects. I'm currently working on adding React and Typescript to my set of skills.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="profile-pic col-12 col-lg-4">
        <%= image_tag 'profile_pic.jpg' %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="skills row">
      <div class="skill-title col-12 col-lg-4">
        <p><strong>Front End</strong></p>
        <div class="dev-icons">
          <i class="devicon-html5-plain-wordmark"></i>
          <i class="devicon-css3-plain-wordmark"></i>
          <i class="devicon-javascript-plain"></i>
          <i class="devicon-sass-original"></i>
          <i class="devicon-bootstrap-plain-wordmark"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-title col-12 col-lg-4">
        <p><strong>Back End</strong></p>
        <div class="dev-icons">
          <i class="devicon-ruby-plain-wordmark"></i>
          <i class="devicon-rails-plain-wordmark"></i>
          <i class="devicon-postgresql-plain-wordmark"></i>
          <i class="devicon-heroku-original-wordmark"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-title col-12 col-lg-4">
        <p><strong>Other Tools</strong></p>
        <div class="dev-icons">
          <i class="devicon-visualstudio-plain"></i>
          <i class="devicon-git-plain"></i>
          <i class="devicon-trello-plain"></i>
          <i class="devicon-github-original"></i>
          <i class="fab fa-figma"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

